title: Rossleigh Court, Northwest corner of 85th Street and Central Park West.

text:
Central Park West, west side, from 85th to 87th Streets, from south-bound drive in Central Park.
The double building at the left houses the Rossleigh Court Apartments, on the N.W. corner of 85th Street, and the Hotel Peter Stuyvesant on the S.W. corner of 86th Street.

February 2, 1929.

P. L. Sperr, Photographer.
title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 85th Street

text:
Central Park: W.P.A. employees removing the 86th Street crosstown car tracks at the western extremity of a transverse road through the park. This view is westward across Central Park West and shows an apartment house on the west side of same between West 86th (right) to 85th Streets.

September 29, 1936.

W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
title: Manhattan: Central Park - Transverse roads.
